title: Bug 4121JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed upon overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The software should not display an out of sync message when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Export a directory (project).  2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).  3. Overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
